    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">Office of <persName>Robbins, Calhoun, &amp; Co.</persName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(center)">Importers and Jobbers in English, French and German Fancy
                Goods,</p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>26, 28 &amp; 30 Vesey Street</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>NEW YORK</placeName>, <date>Sept 19 1865</date></p>
            <p>My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Probably you have<lb/> by this time received a letter from<lb/> the
                Secretary at the Portug. Hebrew<lb/> Congregation at <placeName>New
                    Orleans</placeName><lb/> requesting you to advertise<lb/> in diffr Jewish
                Periodicals of<lb/> this country for a Reader<lb/> of said congregations.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Sojourning now <sic>untill</sic> after<lb/>
                <date>Yom Kipur</date> in this city &amp; stopping<lb/> at <placeName>59
                    International Hotel</placeName> the<lb/> undersigned a member of Board<lb/> of
                Officers of said congregation<lb/> would with pleasure receive any<lb/>
                communication or see personally<lb/> any Candidate to to this place<lb/> You would
                kindly <hi rend="underline">direct</hi> to do<lb/> so to enable me to bring his<lb/>
                Claim before said Board of <add>?</add><lb/> perhaps in this way the means to<lb/>
                come to an arrangement—</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Thank you for all trouble you</p>
            <p rend="Note:">The paper has a printed letterhead, and the “M” in My in the opening
                salutation is printed.</p>
            <pb n="2R"/>
            <p>will take in our behalf.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <add>?</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">most respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">yr very <add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">Philip Runkel</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>63 International Hotel</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>P.S. I forgot to mention that<lb/> our President, <persName>Mr. Levy</persName> has
                requested me to write you these<lb/> Lines!</p>
        </body>
